          怖すぎる、けど渡がいあり
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="syosaipoint">
          <span class="dli-check-circle"><span></span></span>
          <div class="syosaipointbun">
          緑の自然に囲まれて
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='syosaipointmigi'>
        <div class="syosaipoint">
          <span class="dli-check-circle"><span></span></span>
          <div class="syosaipointbun">
          時間がゆったり流れる地域です
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="syosaipoint">
          <span class="dli-check-circle"><span></span></span>
          <div class="syosaipointbun">
          隠れ家飲食店も
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 

